					<p>The 2nd Ministerial Dialogue on Agriculture, Science and Technology was held on 18-19 April 2012 at the Forum for Agricultural Research in Africa (FARA) Secretariat in Accra, Ghana. The Ministerial Dialogue discussed ways to mobilise resources needed to support research, extension and education institutions related to agriculture. The promotion of intra and cross-border collaboration among and in research, extension and education across Africa.You can read the communiqué here:<a href="http://www.fara-africa.org/media/uploads/communique_2nd_annual_ministerial_dialogue.pdf" target="_self">http://www.fara-africa.org/media/uploads/communique_2nd_annual_ministerial_dialogue.pdf</a>(FARA, 24/04/2012)</p>
